Name: MyFamily Memopet Dog Collar Large
Description: MyFamily Memopet Dog Collar Large40-60cm In an ever-changing world, where objects of daily use are increasingly hi-tech, useful, and functional, we decided to make collars, harnesses, and leashes smart and interactive. Imagine the potential of these accessories, useful and hi-tech, capable of storing a pets most important information and keeping it at hand, easily accessible via the memopetID app on your smartphone. What makes this line special is its technology. We have encased an NFC microchip in every collar, harness, and leash, so that they can be connected to your smartphone by simply approaching them. Technology and functionality. The NFC chips inside each memopet accessory interacts with the memopetID app to provide a revolutionary service. It can be used to make an Id for your Pet , which you can also put his medical record and keep up with his medical status. You can also set a reminders for your pet such as appointments and walking time reminders or the food time. It has no GPS.

Name: ZOLUX BARK CONTROL COLLAR ANTI-BARK COLLAR FOR DOG From 15 KG
Description: ZOLUX BARK CONTROL COLLAR ANTI-BARK COLLAR FOR DOG From 15 KGThis anti-bark collar helps to tackle excessive barking.10 progressive stimulation levels and 1 single vibration mode.Warning system: before any electrostatic stimulation, a collar vibration warns the dogDouble barking detection triggered by a combined detection of the vibrations of the vocal cords and of the barking sound.Indicator of excessive barking for easier adaptation of the stimulation level.Watertight 180 g light case.Stainless surgical steel electrodes.1 year manufacturer warranty.2 hours rechargeable batterie.How it works:An internal microphone picks up the sound and the unit is automatically activated. The bark control collar begins by emitting a one-second ultrasonic sound as a warning to the first bark. At the second bark, the collar emits an ultrasonic sound of 2 seconds. From the third bark, the collar emits an ultrasonic sound of 3 seconds and gives a static shock of 2 to 3 seconds. The dog should stop barking. If the dog barks within one minute after the first static shock, the collar sends an ultrasonic sound of 3 seconds and 2-3 seconds of static shock. If the dog stops barking, the collar will reset to the lowest level and repeat the first 3 steps. The shock levels can be adjusted with the supplied screwdriver.

Name: MyFamily Memopet Dog Collar Medium
Description: MyFamily Memopet Dog Collar Medium 40-60cm In an ever-changing world, where objects of daily use are increasingly hi-tech, useful, and functional, we decided to make collars, harnesses, and leashes smart and interactive. Imagine the potential of these accessories, useful and hi-tech, capable of storing a pets most important information and keeping it at hand, easily accessible via the memopetID app on your smartphone. What makes this line special is its technology. We have encased an NFC microchip in every collar, harness, and leash, so that they can be connected to your smartphone by simply approaching them. Technology and functionality. The NFC chips inside each memopet accessory interacts with the memopetID app to provide a revolutionary service. It can be used to make an Id for your Pet , which you can also put his medical record and keep up with his medical status. You can also set a reminders for your pet such as appointments and walking time reminders or the food time. It has no GPS.
